Florence Andiru Nebanda, onye a maara dị ka Florence Nebanda, bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na onye omeiwu Uganda. Ọ bụ nwanyị omebe iwu, na-anọchite anya Butaleja District na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke Uganda
A họpụtara ya n'ọkwa ahụ na Febụwarị 2013, na-anọchi nwanne ya nwanyị nke obere, Cerinah Nebanda, onye nwụrụ n'ọchịchị na Disemba 2012.
Ọ bụ nwa mbụ n'ezinụlọ ụmụ asatọ (otu nwa nwoke na ụmụ nwanyị asaa) a mụrụ ya na Entebbe, na 9 Ọktoba 1986 nye Peter Waiga na Alice Namulwa
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ Ugandan ruo mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na UACE ya na Katikamu SDA Secondary School na Wobulenzi, Luwero district na 2013. Ọ kwagara United Kingdom iji gaa n'ihu na agụmakwụkwọ

Ọ laghachiri Uganda mgbe nwanne ya nwanyị Cerinah Nebanda nwụrụ na Disemba 2012. A kọrọ na o nwere BA na Human Resources Management nke e nwetara na Mahadum nke East London na 2008 na MA na International Human Resources management, na Mahaduma Bedfordshire na United Kingdom.
N'abalị iri na anọ n'ọnwa Disemba n'afọ 2012, Cerinah Nebanda, onye a họpụtara ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu maka Butaleja Women's Constituency nwụrụ na mberede, na-eme ka ọ bụrụ ebe tọgbọrọ n'efu
Na ntuli aka iji mejupụta oche ya, nwanne ya nwanyị nke okenye, Florence Andiru Nebanda meriri na tiketi ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị nke National Resistance Movement
Ọ ga-eje ozi fọdụrụ n'oge ahụ ruo mgbe ntuli aka nke Machị 2016. Ọ bụkwa onye otu Kọmitii na-ahụ maka mmefu ego na ihe gbasara onye isi ala.
Nebanda hụrụ netball n'anya dị ka otu n'ime ihe ntụrụndụ ya, ọ bụ akụkụ nke asọmpi Netball nke ndị omeiwu mgbe ọ nọ na 9th parliament
Ọ na-agụkwa akwụkwọ akụkọ na Bible.
